♪Conflicts are witnessed by the clashing of youths♪

24
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:56,000
♪Brushing against the blade of time♪

25
00:01:56,400 --> 00:02:03,480
♪At the end of the universe, we embark on another journey yet again♪

26
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:15,940
[The Blood of Youth: Quest of Heroic Hearts]

27
00:02:15,980 --> 00:02:18,980
[Episode 16]

28
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:21,310
Waiter!

29
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,800
Is my order ready?

30
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,030
Coming!

31
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:27,560
I heard many people died

32
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:29,080
on the eastern street last night.

33
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,430
Enjoy.

34
00:02:30,470 --> 00:02:31,870
They say it was done by a woman.

35
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,630
A woman?

36
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:37,840
How so?

37
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,560
Did any of them manage to survive?

38
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:40,870
Impossible.

39
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:43,590
The victims were all killed by a single cut on their throats.

40
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:48,000
Someone saw her from afar.

41
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,030
They were terrified.

42
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:53,960
Come. Dig in.

43
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,430
Powerful

44
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,590
and ruthless.

45
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:03,120
Weigui.

46
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,470
Could this

47
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,840
be the Divine Maiden?

48
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,360
I'm not sure.

49
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:17,870
I feel like checking the eastern street out.

50
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,840
If it truly is the Divine Maiden,

51
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:20,960
I want to persuade her

52
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:21,910
to turn over a new leaf.

53
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:26,280
But she and we

54
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,710
are fundamentally different.

55
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:29,750
Even if

56
00:03:29,910 --> 00:03:31,430
she turns into a kind person,

57
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,310
her hands

58
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:36,000
are already tainted with blood.

59
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:39,280
You hail from a righteous sect.

60
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:40,680
The two of you

61
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:42,310
stand on opposite sides.

62
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,590
Perhaps you should give up.

63
00:03:47,150 --> 00:03:47,910
I know.

64
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,310
I just hope

65
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,750
it isn't her doing.

66
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:58,470
Something's wrong

67
00:03:58,630 --> 00:03:59,840
with Hua Xiaohua lately.

68
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:09,710
[Inn]

69
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,400
Xiaohua.

70
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,030
Hua...

71
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:15,910
Hua Xiaohua.

72
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:17,800
Hua Xiaohua.

73
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:34,390
Hua Xiaohua.

74
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:37,750
What are you doing here this late at night?

75
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,630
We were so worried about you.

76
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,630
I came

77
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,040
to find myself a blessed burial spot.

78
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,830
What are you talking about?

79
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:49,950
I am afflicted with a peculiar poison.

80
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,560
I killed innocents.

81
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:54,070
I don't want to live anymore.

82
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:58,120
So, you are the murderer they spoke of on the street.

83
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,070
Were you poisoned in the peach blossom forest?

84
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:09,830
I've tried.

85
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,630
I can't cure myself.

86
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:15,800
You can't,

87
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,160
but your master can.

88
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,360
Find your master

89
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,720
and you will be cured.

90
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,270
My master's exceptional medical knowledge

91
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,160
can cure any ailment in the world.

92
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:26,270
But he's always traveling.

93
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,000
I don't know where he is.

94
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,750
Even if we can't locate your master,

95
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,360
there must be a way to cure you too.

96
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:36,270
That's right.

97
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,720
Perhaps someone can help you.

98
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:51,630
This should be the place.

99
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,040
The expert

100
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,000
you mentioned

101
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,000
lives here?

102
00:05:58,190 --> 00:06:00,120
The elders in my clan once mentioned

103
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,270
that

104
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,360
an expert from Tangmen lived in seclusion in this place.

105
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:04,390
Only he

106
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,630
can remove the poison in Hua Xiaohua.

107
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:12,240
Who dares intrude upon Wangyou Manor?

108
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:17,750
I am Lei Lingze.

109
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,160
My sincerest salutations, Mr. Tang.

110
00:06:20,310 --> 00:06:21,480
We seek your medicine,

111
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,120
Mr. Tang.

112
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,480
To think that one day,

113
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:30,390
people of the Lei's Stronghold would come begging Tangmen for help.

114
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:33,560
I've lived in this manor for many years,

115
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:36,310
with hardly any visitors.

116
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,000
To my surprise,

117
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,950
the first one who shows up

118
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:42,750
is actually my sworn enemy.

119
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:46,270
Great!

120
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,920
Your sect and my clan have fought for many years.

121
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:51,510
We've become both friends and enemies.

122
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:53,000
We're not just enemies.

123
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:55,240
I also do not come with any malice.

124
00:06:55,830 --> 00:06:57,000
My friend's life is hanging

125
00:06:57,270 --> 00:06:58,870
by a thread due to a particular poison.

126
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,720
Please help us, Sir.

127
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,360
How funny.

128
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:06,950
Tangmen is renowned for its poison.

129
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,070
We don't save people.

130
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,950
If you can make poison,

131
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,070
you can also make antidotes.

132
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:12,950
I heard

133
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,240
that you

134
00:07:14,270 --> 00:07:15,310
possess rare talents.

135
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:16,920
Only you

136
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,390
can cure her peculiar ailment.

137
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,870
You are right about that.

138
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:25,160
But

139
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:28,310
why should I help you?

140
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,040
I...

141
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,070
I'm willing to be experimented on.

142
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,800
I see.

143
00:07:47,430 --> 00:07:50,270
You know my rules very well.

144
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,160
Mr. Tang.

145
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:13,360
Both of you came at a great time.

146
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:16,270
[Tangmen Elder]
These are the poisons

147
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,920
I've developed all these years.

148
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:22,680
Venom of Thousand Bugs.

149
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:27,430
Heart-scorching Pill.

150
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,510
Frozen Toad Chilling Powder.

151
00:08:33,910 --> 00:08:34,840
Any one of them

152
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,270
will make you wish

153
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:40,790
you were dead.

154
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,270
If you

155
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:45,000
can test

156
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:47,200
these three poisons for me,

157
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,030
I'll make an antidote

158
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:52,200
for your friend.

159
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,150
Are you sure about it?

160
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:05,840
I hope once I take these poisons,

161
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:07,270
you

162
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,000
will keep your promise.

163
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,910
I am

164
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:12,320
a man of my word.

165
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:34,910
Lei Lingze.

166
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,550
You're awake?

167
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:22,440
Where's Mr. Tang?

168
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,270
You survived those three poisons.

169
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,240
Mr. Tang agreed

170
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,870
to make the antidote for Xiaohua.

171
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:32,840
Good.

172
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:36,320
I knew I could be the strongest swordsman.

173
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:37,510
Mere poison

174
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,320
will not kill me.

175
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,910
God knows how I survived the poison.

176
00:10:46,630 --> 00:10:47,550
I was surprised

177
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,080
at how reckless you were.

178
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:51,670
Reckless?

179
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,440
Would you have done it if it were you?

180
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:58,000
Of course, not.

181
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:02,510
You would've done it.

182
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:03,510
I wouldn't.

183
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:05,790
You most definitely would.

184
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,030
Indeed, people of the Lei's Stronghold

185
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:16,600
are impetuous.

186
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,840
He was willing

187
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:22,750
to ingest such a dangerous poison.

188
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,550
He has been administered the antidote.

189
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:27,960
He will be fine.

190
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:31,360
But it seems like

191
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:33,630
he won't be able

192
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:36,120
to take the other two poisons.

193
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:38,790
Sir,

194
00:11:40,790 --> 00:11:41,910
I can be

195
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,600
your test subject.

196
00:11:44,630 --> 00:11:46,480
You're not from Lei's Stronghold.

197
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,840
Why must you

198
00:11:49,150 --> 00:11:51,360
take the risk in his place?

199
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,840
Sir, you've lived in seclusion

200
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:56,150
because you value peace.

201
00:11:57,870 --> 00:11:59,120
If Lei's Stronghold learns

202
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,270
that he dies here,

203
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:04,510
you'll be in a lot of trouble.

204
00:12:05,390 --> 00:12:06,360
I am an orphan.

205
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:08,240
Why not experiment on me?

206
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,550
Besides,

207
00:12:11,750 --> 00:12:13,080
both the poisoned and he

208
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:15,030
are my close friends.

209
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:20,790
I am willing to take the risk for them.

210
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:24,000
Good.

211
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:25,870
If you insist on

212
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,670
becoming my test subject,

213
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:31,150
so be it.

214
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:58,440
♪How can I make peace when time♪

215
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:01,560
♪Only leaves me with my shadow?♪

216
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:06,520
♪Yet the intertwining bonds in my life♪

217
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:09,800
♪Render me blind♪

218
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:14,720
♪I was once naive and innocent♪

219
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:18,000
♪Seeking a soul with whom to dance♪

220
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:22,960
♪Yet my life is like a wisp of smoke♪

221
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:26,120
♪Scattered by a gust of wind♪

222
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:29,120
♪In this life, I am not destined to be understood♪

223
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,400
♪But misunderstood♪

224
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:34,480
♪I do not know sincerity♪

225
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:39,240
♪If the river of time could flow back to its starting point♪

226
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:42,560
♪Let's not meet again♪

227
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:45,520
♪No one will be able to understand me♪

228
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,600
♪None will go as I wish♪

229
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:50,840
♪How I long for that one moment to last forever♪

230
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:55,560
♪All mortal obsessions turn into dusts of nothingness♪

231
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:58,760
♪Let's not meet in another life♪

232
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:02,440
♪Not in another life♪

233
